Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.92,0:00:07.05,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,It was a small incident that happened to me, Nanoha Takamachi,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.05,0:00:10.51,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,a girl who was supposed to be an ordinary third-grader.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.16,0:00:15.69,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,I believed in the courage within my heart,\Nand I gained magical powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.63,0:00:20.07,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,I wished for a very small feeling to reach its destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:24.94,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,The beginning of the journey must always be so sad,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.94,0:00:28.27,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,but I'm sure the feelings have gotten across.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.28,0:00:33.51,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,So I'm sure {\i0}goodbye{\i1} is the word that begins something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.55,0:00:38.75,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,{\i0}Magical Girl Lyrical Nanoha{\i1} will now begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.61,0:01:00.55,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Cradling my knees in a corner of my room
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.55,0:01:04.08,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,I always shivered from uncertainty
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.08,0:01:11.12,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,I was scared of learning the truth,\Nso I closed the door
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.12,0:01:18.46,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,I found my own place within a kind lie and I fled inside my dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.46,0:01:27.04,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,I dye a sea of loneliness that nobody knows of into a deep blue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.04,0:01:32.81,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,An intense feeling to hide the loneliness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.81,0:01:39.08,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Is continually injuring your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.08,0:01:43.76,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,The secret hidden deep within the eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.76,0:01:48.29,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,To the truth behind the smile that draws me in
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.29,0:01:53.73,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,I will deliver a love so soft
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.73,0:01:58.27,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Right now, a warmth that might break upon touching it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.27,0:02:02.84,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Parts itself from the past, and overflows
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.84,0:02:07.41,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,I'll be by your side forever
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.41,0:02:17.41,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Do not be lured into the somber shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.03,0:02:31.76,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Please, everyone!\NHurry up and escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:40.67,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.95,0:02:44.11,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.19,0:02:52.92,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Fate! Fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.73,0:02:58.92,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.03,0:03:03.97,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Fly! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:53.91,Nanoha Title2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(917,0)\an5\pos(480,240)}{\c&HE9C5A0&}Episode 13
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:53.91,Nanoha Title2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(917,0)\an5\pos(480,473)}{\c&HE9C5A0&}Call My Name
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.53,0:04:08.86,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Looks like the earthquake is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.80,0:04:11.03,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.24,0:04:15.87,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The Garden's destruction is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.87,0:04:18.48,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Everything has been absorbed into the imaginary number plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:21.81,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The dimensional tremor is ending.\NThere are no dimensional faults.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.81,0:04:22.88,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:24.52,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Escaping at Speed Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.52,0:04:26.35,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Returning to our patrol course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:35.29,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Where's Fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,0:04:37.33,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,She's in the brig with Arf.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:40.33,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Since she's a material witness in this incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.33,0:04:42.93,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but she will be detained for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:44.90,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But that's... ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:46.50,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Nanoha, stay still!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.84,0:04:51.41,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,This incident was a major case, where one mistaken step
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.41,0:04:54.88,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,might have caused the creation of a dimensional fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.88,0:04:57.18,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The Time-Space Administration Bureau has to be very careful
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.18,0:04:59.85,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,about the treatment of all involved parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:01.44,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You understand that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:03.95,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.95,0:05:05.89,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Amy, do it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.89,0:05:06.88,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Darn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.27,0:05:23.10,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,And so, all sorts of things came to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.07,0:05:27.01,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,From the day that I met\NYuuno until today...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.01,0:05:30.18,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Now that everything's over, it seems like it all happened in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.91,0:05:33.55,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,We spent several days aboard the {\i1}Arthra{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:37.35,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,until the aftershocks of the dimensional tremor subsided.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:38.65,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Rice bowl...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.27,0:05:59.00,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Since then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.18,0:06:06.05,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You demonstrated outstanding service in the resolution of this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.05,0:06:07.95,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Even if it's a bit informal,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.95,0:06:10.58,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'd like to award you for your distinguished service.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.92,0:06:16.66,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Miss Nanoha Takamachi and Mr. Yuuno Scrya,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.26,0:06:19.53,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.98,0:06:39.68,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Chrono, what's going to happen to Fate now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.68,0:06:43.22,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Though she had her reasons, it's an undeniable fact
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.22,0:06:46.59,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,that she was part of a conspiracy in meddling with the dimensions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.73,0:06:49.39,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That's a felony.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.39,0:06:51.76,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Usually, you get locked up for several centuries, if not more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:53.06,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.06,0:06:54.19,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,However!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.53,0:06:59.04,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The situation is rather special, and it's clear that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:02.67,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,she wasn't party to the dimensional crimes of her own will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:08.35,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,What we have left is to figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.35,0:07:11.01,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,how to get the brass to understand those facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.01,0:07:13.58,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But I'm pretty confident on that score,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.58,0:07:15.49,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,so you don't have to worry at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:17.15,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Chrono...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.15,0:07:19.99,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The Time-Space Administration Bureau isn't a group
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.99,0:07:23.79,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,of cold-hearted people who'd pin a crime on a girl who knew nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:27.23,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,and was just doing her best to grant her mother's wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.37,0:07:34.67,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Chrono... can it be that you're actually a really kind person?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.67,0:07:35.73,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:42.18,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That was just stating the obvious as an Enforcer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.18,0:07:44.11,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,There were no personal feelings involved!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.08,0:07:47.25,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.25,0:07:49.05,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm not embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.05,0:07:51.72,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,What?! Don't laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:56.26,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The dimensional tremor aftershocks will be subsiding soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.26,0:08:01.03,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I think we can get back to your world by tomorrow, Miss Nanoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.30,0:08:02.67,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.67,0:08:07.54,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,However, the route to Midchilda hasn't stabilized quite yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:09.77,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It looks like that will take some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.77,0:08:11.14,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.14,0:08:13.41,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,A few months, maybe half a year...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.41,0:08:17.55,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It looks like it will take that long before we can cruise safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.55,0:08:19.18,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:21.52,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Well, my clan is full of people
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.52,0:08:24.79,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,who wander all over the world in search of archaeological ruins,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.79,0:08:28.33,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,so there really isn't a definite necessity for me to hurry back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.33,0:08:32.40,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But I can't really have you host me on this ship for that long...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.40,0:08:36.10,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Then you can stay at my house, like you have been!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.10,0:08:37.43,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Is that all right, Nanoha?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.43,0:08:38.40,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:40.20,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,As long as you're fine with it, Yuuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:41.44,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Then, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.44,0:08:44.44,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Um, please take good care of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.44,0:08:45.47,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.45,0:08:50.58,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Geez, it's because you slept so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.58,0:08:53.55,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But I was pulling so many all-nighters!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:55.04,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm still sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:09:00.09,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The place called Alhazred that she was aiming for...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.09,0:09:01.79,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You know of it, right, Yuuno?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.79,0:09:04.23,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes, I've heard of it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.23,0:09:07.87,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,They say it existed in previous centuries, by the old calendar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.87,0:09:12.37,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The land where many spells that have been lost now still rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.37,0:09:13.40,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But they also say
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:17.21,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,that it fell into a dimensional fault long ago and fell to ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.21,0:09:18.51,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Hey there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:22.71,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,They say that there is no wish you can leave ungranted
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.71,0:09:26.85,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,using the powers of the secret spells of Alhazred,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.85,0:09:29.29,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,with all sorts of magic in its ultimate state.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:34.25,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Magic that can turn back time and space, and even rewrite the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.79,0:09:38.43,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Magic that can bring back to the living a life that has been lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:40.40,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Those were the things she wanted, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.40,0:09:41.37,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.37,0:09:45.14,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But everyone who learns magic knows for a fact
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.14,0:09:49.64,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,that turning back time and raising the dead is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.64,0:09:52.54,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That is why, seeking both of those ideals,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.54,0:09:56.25,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,she could only rely on such a fairy-tale legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.25,0:09:58.32,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,She had no choice but to rely on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:10:03.52,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But a mage of that level was risking her life in that search.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.52,0:10:09.26,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Perhaps she really had found the path to Alhazred.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.93,0:10:12.29,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Though there's no way for us to know now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.57,0:10:21.37,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, this mealtime story has gotten quite long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.37,0:10:23.21,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Let's finish our meals before they get cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.21,0:10:27.54,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm sure this will be your last meal aboard the {\i1}Arthra{\i0}, Nanoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:28.48,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:30.35,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,If parting ways makes you lonely,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:32.92,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,you should honestly just come out and say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:34.95,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Chrono, you're so shy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.95,0:10:36.25,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.25,0:10:40.26,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Nanoha, you can always come by and visit us, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:42.26,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes! Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.26,0:10:45.70,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Amy! The {\i1}Arthra{\i0} is not a playground!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:47.86,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Well now, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:51.40,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,When our mission is to patrol, we're always full of idle time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:53.63,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Ca... Captain! You as well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.51,0:10:59.31,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,And the morning where Yuuno and I were going home...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:03.41,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Well... thank you so much for everything you did this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.41,0:11:05.21,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,We appreciated your support.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.86,0:11:15.03,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'll inform you of Fate's treatment when it's been decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.03,0:11:18.23,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It's all right, I'll make sure that nothing bad happens to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.23,0:11:20.40,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah... thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:23.97,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yuuno, when you want to go back, please contact us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.97,0:11:25.54,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'll let you use our gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.54,0:11:27.80,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes! Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:31.38,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Then, I guess we're about ready to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.38,0:11:32.94,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.94,0:11:34.00,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:39.48,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'll see you again, Chrono,\NMiss Amy, Miss Lindy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.33,0:11:58.84,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Should we go home now, Yuuno?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.84,0:11:59.96,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.31,0:12:09.68,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.52,0:12:13.85,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Nanoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.85,0:12:17.25,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,And what comes back is my everyday life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.39,0:12:19.86,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,It's the same as it had always been,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.86,0:12:21.69,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,but adding everything that has happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:22.96,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Mom, I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.69,0:12:24.59,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,everyday life is just a little bit different from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.63,0:12:26.69,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.03,0:12:29.47,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Were you a good girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:30.43,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.61,0:12:37.67,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Nanoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.67,0:12:38.90,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE1E1E1&}Nanoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.58,0:12:45.34,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm home! I came back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:51.32,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,The time that you're engrossed in something,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.32,0:12:55.28,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,after it's all over, seems like a fleeting moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.93,0:13:05.46,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,But in my heart, it surely remains true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.37,0:13:10.83,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,How we met... how desperate I was... all sorts of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:27.59,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since I slept in my own bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.59,0:13:30.46,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yuuno, you should rest up tonight too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.46,0:13:31.66,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.66,0:13:34.60,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Thanks for all the hard work,\NRaising Heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.62,0:13:54.71,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Thank you for all the hard work, Nanoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.89,0:14:06.35,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,The one thing that's still on my mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.46,0:14:11.49,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,About that girl with the gentle eyes, that must surely be very kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.45,0:14:27.71,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Several days later...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.94,0:14:53.45,Nanoha Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\an5\frz6.941\pos(439,167)}{\fs37.5\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Incoming Call
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.94,0:14:53.45,Nanoha Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\an5\frz7.41\pos(478.667,383)}{\fs32\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Time-Space\NAdministration Bureau
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:56.41,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is Nanoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.78,0:15:01.89,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.89,0:15:04.49,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's been officially decided on a few moments ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.49,0:15:07.22,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Fate will be transferred over to headquarters,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.22,0:15:10.49,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,and there she will face questioning and a trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.49,0:15:15.13,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Fate will probably—no, almost definitely—be acquitted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.13,0:15:16.20,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Everything will be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:19.80,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Because Chrono was working overtime to gather all the evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.80,0:15:23.54,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Amy! You don't have to mention unnecessary information like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.54,0:15:25.48,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Chrono!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.71,0:15:31.18,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The questioning, trial, and everything else will take quite a bit of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.18,0:15:32.78,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But, before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:33.82,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:35.12,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:36.89,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:37.95,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.02,0:15:40.51,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,What's up, Nanoha?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.56,0:15:45.53,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Fate is going to be transferred to headquarters for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.53,0:15:49.30,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But before that, I can see her for just a little bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:50.53,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.53,0:15:53.23,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,She's saying that she wants to see me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.93,0:16:22.02,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.54,0:16:36.01,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,We don't have much time, but sit down and have a talk for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:37.71,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,We'll be over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:39.64,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.28,0:16:42.55,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.98,0:17:14.12,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,There were so many things\NI wanted to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.12,0:17:15.65,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But it's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.65,0:17:19.19,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,When I saw your face, Fate,\NI forgot all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.19,0:17:22.83,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I... let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:25.32,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I can't put it into words well, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:28.66,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But I was really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.17,0:17:32.23,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That you looked at me so straightforwardly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:36.76,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I thought that it would be great if we could be friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.71,0:17:41.64,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But today, you have to head out right after this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.41,0:17:46.94,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That's true. It will be a pretty long trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:49.65,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But I can see you again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.06,0:17:59.76,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It's a bit sad, but I can finally begin to be my own self.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:04.63,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I had you come here so that\NI could give you an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.30,0:18:12.98,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The words that you told me...\NThat you wanted to be my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:14.38,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.38,0:18:17.71,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,If it's possible for me... if you're okay with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:21.72,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But I don't know what I should be doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.32,0:18:24.29,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,So I want you to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:26.65,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,How do you become a friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.37,0:18:36.89,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:40.90,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It's really easy to become friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.91,0:18:45.67,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Call me by my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:49.25,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,In the beginning, that's all you have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.25,0:18:52.35,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Not "you" or "hey, you" or anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.35,0:18:54.15,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Look directly at the person's eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:56.68,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,and clearly call them by their name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.09,0:19:00.72,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm Nanoha Takamachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.72,0:19:01.82,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Call me Nanoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.86,0:19:04.16,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Nanoha...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:05.82,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:08.83,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Nanoha...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.83,0:19:10.03,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.13,0:19:12.30,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Nanoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.27,0:19:14.43,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.71,0:19:21.74,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Nanoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.71,0:19:24.04,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:26.38,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Nanoha...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.42,0:19:32.45,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.12,0:19:37.25,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Your hands are so warm, Nanoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:45.83,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,There's something that I figured out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.84,0:19:51.07,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,When a friend is crying, you're sad in the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.94,0:19:53.50,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:56.91,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Nanoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.91,0:20:00.52,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,We'll part for now, but I'm sure we'll see each other again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.52,0:20:04.82,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,When that happens, can I call you by your name again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.82,0:20:06.95,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.86,0:20:10.76,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,When I want to see you,\NI'm sure to be calling your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.16,0:20:15.93,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,So Nanoha, I want you to call for me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.37,0:20:19.80,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,If something is troubling you, Nanoha...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.80,0:20:23.40,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that this time,\NI will save you, Nanoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.05,0:20:39.39,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Your girl over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.39,0:20:40.92,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Nanoha...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.92,0:20:43.26,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,She sure is a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:46.56,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Fate is smiling so much right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.27,0:21:00.44,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It's time. Are you about done?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.88,0:21:04.21,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.09,0:21:16.33,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,This is all I have that I can use as a token of our memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.33,0:21:18.09,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Then, I should too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.84,0:21:30.86,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Nanoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.84,0:21:33.17,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.48,0:21:36.31,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm sure once again...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.31,0:21:38.41,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I'm sure once again...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.49,0:21:45.49,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.49,0:21:47.48,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Miss Arf, you stay well too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.12,0:21:51.09,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Thanks for everything,\NNanoha, Yuuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.09,0:21:53.00,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'm on my way too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.00,0:21:54.53,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,See you later, Chrono!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.53,0:21:55.62,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.58,0:22:13.85,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye, see you later...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.25,0:22:16.84,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Chrono...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.85,0:22:19.94,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Miss Arf...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.42,0:22:23.82,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.13,0:23:07.43,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Nanoha?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.17,0:23:11.16,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.57,0:23:14.14,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Make a little wish
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.14,0:23:19.64,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Even though at times\NI'll trip or get lost
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.08,0:23:30.08,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Because you're with me, I can continue to smile and be energetic
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.33,0:23:42.07,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Ah, don't look down as you walk, it's all right
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.07,0:23:49.65,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,The courage that you handed to me that day is still in my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.78,0:23:46.98,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Nanoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.34,0:23:49.65,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.65,0:23:57.02,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Each time I blink, more kindness is born
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.02,0:24:05.26,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,See, this love is something I want to nurture always, forever
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.26,0:24:07.10,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Make a little wish
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.10,0:24:13.04,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Wearing the lemon-colored\Ndrops from the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.04,0:24:20.04,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,I want to keep glimmering with a twinkle and keep on as your energy
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.04,0:24:21.48,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Make a little wish
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.48,0:24:27.38,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,On rainy days and dawns\Nwhen I couldn't fall asleep
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.38,0:24:34.42,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Because you were here with me,\NI was able to smile my best
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.42,0:24:38.12,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Just like this
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.40,0:24:49.61,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Whenever we're apart, I still have something I can believe in
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.61,0:24:58.15,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,See, our hearts are always,\Nsurely together as one
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.15,0:24:59.68,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Make a little wish
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.68,0:25:05.56,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Collecting the lemon-colored\Ndrops from the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.56,0:25:12.63,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Let's turn them into warm tears, and make them spices for smiles
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.63,0:25:14.23,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Make a little wish
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.23,0:25:20.10,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Even though at times\NI'll trip or get lost
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.10,0:25:30.10,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Because you're with me, I can continue to smile and be energetic
